Package: infForest
Type: Package
Title: Inference Forests: Nonparametric Inference with Tree Ensembles
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nathaniel", "O'Connell", 
                  email = "nathaniel.oconnell@wfusm.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Provides a complete framework for nonparametric effect estimation 
    and inference from random forests. Fits inference forests with standardized 
    splitting criteria and softmax variable selection, extracts effect estimates 
    for binary and continuous predictors on any outcome type, constructs 
    nonlinear effect curves, estimates interactions of arbitrary order, and 
    provides valid confidence intervals via procedure-aligned synthetic 
    resampling (PASR). Prediction intervals for deployed forests are also 
    supported. Based on the theoretical framework of O'Connell (2026).
